{
  "video_id": "UoX-YihV_ew",
  "title": "Margaret Stewart: How YouTube thinks about copyright",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "So, if you&#39;re in the audience today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "or maybe you&#39;re watching this talk in some other time or place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "you are a participant in the digital rights ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "Whether you&#39;re an artist, a technologist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "a lawyer or a fan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "the handling of copyright directly impacts your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "Rights management is no longer"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "simply a question of ownership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a complex web of relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "and a critical part of our cultural landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "YouTube cares deeply about the rights of content owners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "but in order to give them choices about what they can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "with copies, mashups and more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "we need to first identify"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "when copyrighted material is uploaded to our site."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at a specific video so you can see how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, recording artist Chris Brown"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "released the official video of his single \"Forever.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "A fan saw it on TV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "recorded it with her camera phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "and uploaded it to YouTube."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "Because Sony Music had registered Chris Brown&#39;s video"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "in our Content ID system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "within seconds of attempting to upload the video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "the copy was detected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "giving Sony the choice of what to do next."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "But how do we know that the user&#39;s video was a copy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "Well, it starts with content owners"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "delivering assets into our database,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "along with a usage policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "that tells us what to do when we find a match."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "We compare each upload"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "against all of the reference files in our database."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "This heat map is going to show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "how the brain of the system works."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "Here we can see the original reference file"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "being compared to the user generated content."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "The system compares every moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "of one to the other to see if there&#39;s a match."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "This means that we can identify a match"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "even if the copy used is just a portion of the original file,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "plays it in slow motion"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "and has degraded audio and video quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "And we do this every time"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "that a video is uploaded to YouTube."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s over 20 hours of video every minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "When we find a match,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "we apply the policy that the rights owner has set down."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "And the scale and the speed of this system"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "is truly breathtaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not just talking about a few videos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re talking about over"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "100 years of video every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "between new uploads and the legacy scans"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "we regularly do across all of the content on the site."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "When we compare those hundred years of video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re comparing it against millions"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "of reference files in our database."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "It would be like 36,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "staring at 36,000 monitors"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "each and every day, without so much as a coffee break."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "Now, what do we do when we find a match?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "Well, most rights owners, instead of blocking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "will allow the copy to be published."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "And then they benefit through the exposure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "advertising and linked sales."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "Remember Chris Brown&#39;s video \"Forever\"?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "Well, it had its day in the sun and then it dropped off the charts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "and that looked like the end of the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "but sometime last year, a young couple got married."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "This is their wedding video."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "You may have seen it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s amazing about this is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "if the processional of the wedding was this much fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "can you imagine how much fun the reception must have been?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "I mean, who are these people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "I totally want to go to that wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "So their little wedding video went on"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "to get over 40 million views."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "And instead of Sony blocking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "they allowed the upload to occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "And they put advertising against it"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "and linked from it to iTunes."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "And the song, 18 months old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "went back to number four on the iTunes charts."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "So Sony is generating revenue from both of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "And Jill and Kevin, the happy couple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "they came back from their honeymoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "and found that their video had gone crazy viral."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;ve ended up on a bunch of talk shows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve used it as an opportunity to make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "The video&#39;s inspired over 26,000 dollars in donations"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "to end domestic violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "The \"JK Wedding [Entrance] Dance\" became so popular"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "that NBC parodied it on the season finale of \"The Office,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "which just goes to show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s truly an ecosystem of culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s not just amateurs borrowing from big studios,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "but sometimes big studios borrowing back."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "By empowering choice, we can create a culture of opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "And all it took to change things around"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "was to allow for choice through rights identification."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "So why has no one ever solved this problem before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because it&#39;s a big problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s complicated and messy."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not uncommon for a single video"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "to have multiple rights owners."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s musical labels."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s multiple music publishers."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "And each of these can vary by country."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s lots of cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "where we have more than one work mashed together."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "So we have to manage many claims"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "to the same video."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "YouTube&#39;s Content ID system addresses all of these cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "But the system only works through"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "the participation of rights owners."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "If you have content that others are uploading to YouTube,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "you should register in the Content ID system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "and then you&#39;ll have the choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "about how your content is used."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "And think carefully about the policies that you attach to that content."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "By simply blocking all reuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll miss out on new art forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "new audiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "new distribution channels"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "and new revenue streams."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just about dollars and impressions."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "Just look at all the joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "that was spread through progressive rights management"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "and new technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "And I think we can all agree that joy is definitely an idea worth spreading."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}